name: Artificial Imagination #2
description:
Text to Image synthesis (CLIP & VQGan)

This piece is the 2nd from a collection of 4 I made using the text prompt 'Artificial Imagination'.


I developed a particular technique that allowed me to guide the overall composition of a piece. 

Its a collage style which I've become fascinated with - the themes and ideas from the prompt come through in random yet connected ways - creating an overall picture with a narrative.  For me these are enjoyable to just sit and stare at.
